Strategic advantages
The Latin brew kings have succeeded because they dominate the beer business in
their respective countries and/or have strong showings in their own country and
other selected markets. Their principal markets offer greater potential growth
than the mature markets in the U.S., Canada, and Western Europe, and their
success has been aided by diversifying outside the beer business.

AmBev's second-quarter performance illustrates the benefits of Latin American
beer investing. Its profit rose 34%, and its revenue climbed 13% from the
year-ago period.

http://www.fool.com/investing/general/2009/08/24/big-beer-is-the-next-big-growt
